name: Fidelity Canadian High Dividend ETF
longDescription: Fidelity Canadian High Dividend Index ETF (Fund) seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Fidelity Canada Canadian High Dividend Index (Index). The Fund invests primarily in dividend paying equity securities of Canadian companies.
